comments: George (LAC) does not release his shot attempt before the expiration of the shot clock.
Powell (LAC) initiates more than marginal contact to Gordon's (DEN) arm during his shot attempt at the basket.
Mann (LAC) brings his hands toward Caldwell-Pope (DEN) and marginal contact occurs as Mann releases away to roll.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) extends both hands forward and initiates contact with George (LAC) during the drive, affecting his SQBR.  The illegal contact occurs before George's upward shooting motion.
Jackson (DEN) goes to, not through, Mann's (LAC) space and marginal contact occurs as Jackson releases away during the drive.
Leonard (LAC) keeps his hand on the side of the ball in-between dribbles.
George (LAC) reaches in and makes marginal contact with Jokic's (DEN) arm before he makes the pass.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) initiates illegal body contact and steps forward into George's (LAC) right leg and the contact affects his jump shot attempt.
Mann (LAC) commits a take foul on Jackson (DEN).
Porter Jr. (DEN) brings his arm toward Leonard's (LAC) front and marginal contact occurs at the start of Leonard's drive.

Replay review of the foul called on Porter Jr. (DEN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Porter Jr. (DEN) extends his right hand and initiates contact with Leonard's (LAC) back, affecting his ability to finish at the rim.
Leonard (LAC) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Caldwell-Pope (DEN) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
George (LAC) gathers the ball and takes three steps to the basket.
Jokic (DEN) reaches for the loose ball and brushes George's (LAC) hand and the contact is incidental.
Powell (LAC) initiates contact with Jokic's (DEN) arm and affects his SQBR.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) briefly has a hand placed at George's (LAC) side and he grazes his leg during the jump shot attempt.  The contact during George's shooting motion is marginal.
George's (LAC) shot attempt is wedged between the rim and the backboard and play resumes with a jump ball at center circle.
